## VI. NEXT PRIORITY QUEUE

Per `FUTURE_WORKS.md §VII` and `ARCHITECTURAL_DIRECTIVE Tier 2`:

1. **IDX-006 — Rubber Band Effect** *(Reactor integration)*: Force a position jump beyond Overton Spread → Chaos Modifier → Stability drain → Estate rebellion snap-back.
2. **IDX-007 — Glacial Shift** *(Chronos integration)*: `position` drifts toward [center](file:///c:/Users/zephy/Documents/Brinkmanship/brinkmanship_engine/src/ideology_matrix.rs#344-349) at a rate governed by Estate influence shifts. Direct single-turn matrix jumps are mechanically prohibited.
3. **DIP-002 — AI Parity**: Rival actors autonomously navigate the Structural Matrix.
4. **NAR-001 — Sovereign Introduction Tutorial**: Cannot ship without IDX-006/007 implemented first.

